# VCPomodoro Project Rules

## Terminal Commands
- Don't use `cd` to change to the project root if already there - the shell persists between commands
- The project root is `/Users/dzlob/proj/personal/vc-pomodoro`

## Project Info
- This is a macOS menu bar Pomodoro timer app built with Swift/SwiftUI
- Uses osascript for notifications (works without paid Apple Developer account)
- Global hotkey: Cmd+Shift+P to start/pause timer

